<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルビア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rubia</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Caius</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まったく。
ああいう思い込み激しい人は
嫌になっちゃうわ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Honestly. I can't stand people who
just jump to conclusions like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Will come back to this after having more context.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まあまあ。
あの人も悪気はなかったんだしさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now, now. They didn't seem like bad people.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんな事わかってるわよ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I know that already!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ははっ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Haha.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なに笑ってるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you laughing for?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルビアくらいなもんだよな。
オレに対しても普通の人と同じように
怒ったりしてくれるの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's a you thing. You get angry at me
just like you would a normal person.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なに変なこと言ってるのよ？
カイウスがバカな事するんだから
怒るのは当たり前じゃない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why are you saying something weird?
If you say something stupid, of course
I'm gonna get angry!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……そうだな。
そういうもんだよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Yeah. That's how it is.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……？
変なカイウス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...?
Caius, you're weird.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
